<!-- 
    The statistics-view.ejs file provides a selection
    of different statistic view buttons that the user
    can choose to view different statistics in the
    database. Each view button allows the user to see
    the entity type associated with that button in the
    Patient Care Manager database. There are three 
    statistics views: Patient Risk Index, Providers
    Caring for Patients, and Providers and Treatments.
    An "Exit" option is provided to bring the user back 
    to the home page.
